    <h3>Checklist for Forming Producer Company</h3>
    <ul class="a">
        <li>1. A minimum capital of Rs. 5 lakhs</li>
        <li>2. A minimum of 5 directors and a maximum of 15 directors are required</li>
        <li>3. It cannot be converted into a public company</li>

    </ul>

